MOF T - bill , 10 - yr JGB offers likely in Jan - traders . Japan ' s Ministry of Finance ( MOF ) is likely to offer six - month Treasury bills on January 8 and 10 - year bonds on January 9 , both through price - competitive auctions , traders said on Monday . The size of the T - bill offer is expected to be about 1 . 5 trillion yen , as 1 . 5 trillion yen worth of six - month Treasury bills are due on January 13 , they said . Japan ' s capital market closes for New Year holidays on Monday and will reopen on January 6 . 
